1
00:00:59,439 --> 00:01:01,079
Have you found Mr. Chu?

2
00:01:01,359 --> 00:01:01,799
No.

3
00:01:03,079 --> 00:01:04,280
Where did he go?

4
00:01:04,959 --> 00:01:06,280
Master, the opening is about to start.

5
00:01:06,519 --> 00:01:07,200
Let's go.

6
00:01:14,200 --> 00:01:15,840
Chu Mo, the painter.

7
00:01:16,280 --> 00:01:17,439
Butterfly, the killer.

8
00:01:18,120 --> 00:01:18,680
So different.

9
00:01:19,319 --> 00:01:20,400
Is he mentally ill?

10
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,560
Hello, is Chu Mo really the Butterfly?

11
00:01:23,000 --> 00:01:24,480
Does Chu Mo have a backup plan for exposing himself?

12
00:01:24,879 --> 00:01:26,480
Is this his way of drawing attention to his solo exhibition?

13
00:01:26,680 --> 00:01:28,200
May I ask what exactly is your relationship with Chu Mo?

14
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:30,040
How many people has Chu Mo killed?

15
00:01:32,319 --> 00:01:32,840
Everyone,

16
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:34,799
perhaps Mr. Chu

17
00:01:34,799 --> 00:01:35,920
has done many wrong things before,

18
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:38,000
but I also want everyone to know

19
00:01:38,159 --> 00:01:39,760
what Mr. Chu is like in my eyes.

20
00:01:41,000 --> 00:01:43,239
Chu Mo, he is a good teacher to me,

21
00:01:43,519 --> 00:01:44,519
and a good friend.

22
00:01:45,120 --> 00:01:46,760
The first time I saw him,

23
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:49,799
I thought he was elegant

24
00:01:50,319 --> 00:01:51,400
and free.

25
00:01:52,680 --> 00:01:54,519
Nothing in the world

26
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,400
could affect him.

27
00:01:56,920 --> 00:01:57,879
He's kind.

28
00:01:58,719 --> 00:01:59,719
He's my benefactor.

29
00:02:00,159 --> 00:02:01,000
He's willing to help.

30
00:02:01,439 --> 00:02:02,959
He can find the strengths of everyone.

31
00:02:03,280 --> 00:02:04,599
When did you know he was the butterfly?

32
00:02:05,000 --> 00:02:06,040
Does it matter?

33
00:02:06,519 --> 00:02:07,200
Of course.

34
00:02:07,480 --> 00:02:08,840
He is an international felon.

35
00:02:09,680 --> 00:02:10,840
What's your relationship with him?

36
00:02:11,199 --> 00:02:11,960
What do you know?

37
00:02:23,360 --> 00:02:24,080
Who is this?

38
00:02:25,319 --> 00:02:27,120
He is Paul Gourmand, a tobacco tycoon.

39
00:02:27,280 --> 00:02:28,000
I interviewed him.

40
00:02:28,560 --> 00:02:29,360
He is a philanthropist.

41
00:02:30,479 --> 00:02:31,319
So this is...

42
00:02:31,800 --> 00:02:32,719
Human trafficking.

43
00:02:32,840 --> 00:02:33,680
Chumo exposed himself

44
00:02:33,680 --> 00:02:35,319
to reveal the true face of Paul Gourmand,

45
00:02:35,319 --> 00:02:36,639
the real killer.

46
00:02:36,639 --> 00:02:38,039
Look, there's something in the eye.

47
00:02:38,400 --> 00:02:39,199
That's a totem.

48
00:02:39,719 --> 00:02:41,560
The one who killed Bell six years ago was Paul Gourmand.

49
00:02:45,120 --> 00:02:46,039
He also did this.

50
00:02:46,039 --> 00:02:47,360
He actually did this.

51
00:02:51,919 --> 00:02:52,639
I'm Jiang Yue,

52
00:02:54,560 --> 00:02:55,960
Chairman of 3Z Group.

53
00:02:55,960 --> 00:02:57,400
Jiang Changfa is my father.

54
00:03:00,000 --> 00:03:00,560
At the same time,

55
00:03:02,080 --> 00:03:03,319
he is also Paul Gourmand,

56
00:03:03,319 --> 00:03:05,639
the head of human trafficking in Asia.

57
00:03:06,319 --> 00:03:07,240
Sixteen years ago,

58
00:03:08,800 --> 00:03:10,800
my father began to take this irreversible road.

59
00:03:12,960 --> 00:03:14,840
My mother discovered their crimes

60
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:17,280
and wanted to expose them.

61
00:03:18,759 --> 00:03:20,680
She was burned to death by Jiang Changfa.

62
00:03:23,479 --> 00:03:24,599
How could he do that?

63
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,879
Professor Chu.

64
00:03:34,360 --> 00:03:35,680
Miss Lu, please answer.

65
00:03:35,680 --> 00:03:36,439
What's going on?

66
00:03:40,319 --> 00:03:41,199
Why are you so slow?

67
00:03:44,680 --> 00:03:45,360
What are you doing?

68
00:03:46,719 --> 00:03:48,240
You're playing dumb with me.

69
00:03:49,000 --> 00:03:50,680
I won't be grateful for what you did.

70
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:51,680
I don't need you to be grateful.

71
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:53,280
Then you must be tired of living.

72
00:03:53,919 --> 00:03:54,479
You want to die?

73
00:03:57,080 --> 00:03:57,840
You're right about half of it.

74
00:04:01,120 --> 00:04:02,280
It's all my choice.

75
00:04:03,400 --> 00:04:04,360
It has nothing to do with you.

76
00:04:04,879 --> 00:04:05,800
You don't need to feel guilty.

77
00:04:08,400 --> 00:04:09,000
Besides,

78
00:04:11,919 --> 00:04:12,719
fulfilling others

79
00:04:13,479 --> 00:04:15,039
is also worth living for me.

80
00:04:19,480 --> 00:04:19,920
Don't move.

81
00:04:39,160 --> 00:04:40,600
We've confirmed that he is the Butterfly.

82
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,279
Good job.

83
00:04:55,279 --> 00:04:56,120
Sacrifice.

84
00:05:00,879 --> 00:05:03,519
Who would sacrifice themselves

85
00:05:04,120 --> 00:05:05,120
to fulfill others?

86
00:05:14,079 --> 00:05:14,519
Jiang Yue,

87
00:05:17,959 --> 00:05:19,079
be happy with Qi.

88
00:05:49,639 --> 00:05:50,120
Hello,

89
00:05:51,079 --> 00:05:51,879
I'm Chu Mo,

90
00:05:52,600 --> 00:05:53,240
a painter.

91
00:06:02,680 --> 00:06:03,160
Speak!

92
00:06:03,680 --> 00:06:04,120
Master,

93
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:05,160
Miss was taken away by Mr.

94
00:06:13,720 --> 00:06:15,720
We really are of one mind.

95
00:06:18,360 --> 00:06:19,480
We can meet here.

96
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,199
Let Qi Qi go.

97
00:06:25,680 --> 00:06:26,160
Okay.

98
00:06:27,399 --> 00:06:28,360
You go kill Gu Lan.

99
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,600
Our business

100
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:31,920
shouldn't involve others.

101
00:06:33,160 --> 00:06:33,759
I'll stay.

102
00:06:35,120 --> 00:06:35,800
Let the outsider go.

103
00:06:49,040 --> 00:06:49,480
Go.

104
00:06:58,279 --> 00:06:58,879
Jiang Yue.

105
00:07:00,199 --> 00:07:02,560
I don't care what Gu Lan told you.

106
00:07:02,560 --> 00:07:03,279
remember,

107
00:07:04,560 --> 00:07:07,199
my blood flows in your veins.

108
00:07:09,360 --> 00:07:11,160
We are always a family.

109
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:13,600
I

110
00:07:14,279 --> 00:07:15,800
am your only family

111
00:07:15,800 --> 00:07:17,160
in this world.

112
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:19,240
Kill Gu Lan,

113
00:07:19,920 --> 00:07:21,639
and we can rise again.

114
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:23,839
You can still enjoy wealth and honor.

115
00:07:24,720 --> 00:07:25,199
Father,

116
00:07:27,439 --> 00:07:29,639
I never wanted wealth and honor.

117
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:32,079
I don't want to rise again.

118
00:07:38,279 --> 00:07:38,920
What do you want?

119
00:07:39,319 --> 00:07:39,720
Family.

120
00:07:42,240 --> 00:07:43,480
A complete family.

121
00:07:46,160 --> 00:07:46,560
Fine.

122
00:07:48,839 --> 00:07:50,480
I can give you a complete family.

123
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:52,600
Don't you just want to be with Lu Qi?

124
00:07:53,920 --> 00:07:55,639
But now I have to tell you a secret.

125
00:07:59,319 --> 00:08:01,920
How do you think Lu Qi's father died?

126
00:08:05,920 --> 00:08:06,519
Maybe

127
00:08:09,439 --> 00:08:12,160
a few bottles of wine and a driver

128
00:08:12,279 --> 00:08:13,160
plus some money

129
00:08:14,519 --> 00:08:17,079
will make Chen Yuan marry into our family.

130
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,120
I've been teaching you.

131
00:08:22,279 --> 00:08:23,519
Now you know.

132
00:08:24,959 --> 00:08:28,680
You're the son of Lu Qi's father's murderer.

133
00:08:31,040 --> 00:08:32,039
Do you think she'll still be with you

134
00:08:32,039 --> 00:08:33,200
when she finds out?

135
00:08:36,159 --> 00:08:37,519
As long as you kill Gu Lan,

136
00:08:38,639 --> 00:08:39,960
I will help you

137
00:08:39,960 --> 00:08:41,039
forever.

138
00:08:42,639 --> 00:08:43,279
Then,

139
00:08:46,120 --> 00:08:47,240
you can form

140
00:08:47,279 --> 00:08:49,000
a happy family with Lu Qi,

141
00:08:53,759 --> 00:08:55,240
and have a bunch of lovely children.

142
00:09:01,759 --> 00:09:02,720
It will be

143
00:09:04,399 --> 00:09:05,279
so warm and cozy.

144
00:09:05,639 --> 00:09:07,000
I know what you want.

145
00:09:09,519 --> 00:09:10,559
I think this is

146
00:09:12,960 --> 00:09:14,200
what your mother wanted you

147
00:09:14,200 --> 00:09:15,320
to have.

148
00:09:19,360 --> 00:09:20,120
Jiang Changfa,

149
00:09:21,320 --> 00:09:22,320
you still want to

150
00:09:23,720 --> 00:09:25,320
control me by using

151
00:09:25,559 --> 00:09:26,480
my mother.

152
00:09:29,039 --> 00:09:30,320
I should have killed you,

153
00:09:40,080 --> 00:09:41,000
but I can't.

154
00:09:45,120 --> 00:09:46,240
Because you are my father.

155
00:09:50,360 --> 00:09:51,759
I don't want to be like you.

156
00:10:00,200 --> 00:10:01,799
Do you know why I listened to you?

157
00:10:03,759 --> 00:10:04,879
It's because of my mother.

158
00:10:07,000 --> 00:10:07,759
When I knew

159
00:10:10,000 --> 00:10:11,960
my mother's death was related to you,

160
00:10:15,000 --> 00:10:16,120
do you know how desperate I was?

161
00:10:18,000 --> 00:10:19,200
Because my mother knew

162
00:10:19,240 --> 00:10:20,240
the secret of the totem,

163
00:10:20,679 --> 00:10:21,799
she was killed by my father.

164
00:10:23,519 --> 00:10:25,039
I want you to tell me yourself.

165
00:10:25,879 --> 00:10:26,399
Yes,

166
00:10:27,519 --> 00:10:28,559
or not?

167
00:10:35,399 --> 00:10:36,200
You dare not.

168
00:10:42,480 --> 00:10:44,320
It's no use saying anything now.

169
00:10:51,279 --> 00:10:52,080
Jiang Changfa,

170
00:10:55,120 --> 00:10:56,639
I just want to be an ordinary person.

171
00:10:58,360 --> 00:11:00,039
If you have any conscience,

172
00:11:02,159 --> 00:11:03,000
just let me go.

173
00:11:08,639 --> 00:11:09,200
Otherwise,

174
00:11:16,200 --> 00:11:16,960
just kill me.

175
00:11:52,919 --> 00:11:53,519
Jiang Yue.

176
00:11:54,480 --> 00:11:55,039
Qi Qi.

177
00:11:55,720 --> 00:11:56,799
You two are brother and sister.

178
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,279
Be closer in the future.

179
00:12:27,919 --> 00:12:28,399
Let's go.

180
00:12:33,919 --> 00:12:34,639
Jiang Yue,

181
00:12:35,919 --> 00:12:38,639
I feel ashamed about your mother's death.

182
00:12:39,840 --> 00:12:41,039
I just wanted to burn

183
00:12:41,039 --> 00:12:42,120
those paintings that might

184
00:12:42,120 --> 00:12:43,960
contain information about the totems.

185
00:12:44,440 --> 00:12:46,559
But your mother sacrificed herself

186
00:12:47,360 --> 00:12:48,679
to awaken my conscience.

187
00:12:50,519 --> 00:12:52,960
I have paid the price for my mistakes.

188
00:12:54,039 --> 00:12:55,759
I hope you can get over it soon

189
00:12:56,279 --> 00:12:57,679
and start a new life.

190
00:13:09,279 --> 00:13:09,720
Master.

191
00:13:12,000 --> 00:13:13,039
Don't call me that anymore.

192
00:13:15,919 --> 00:13:16,200
Brother,

193
00:13:19,919 --> 00:13:21,000
this is the card you gave to Miss.
